SIMPLE: unprejudiced
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unprejudiced
<hw>Un*prej"u*diced</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Not prejudiced; free from undue bias or prepossession; not
preoccupied by opinion; impartial; <as>as, an <ex>unprejudiced</ex>
mind; an <ex>unprejudiced</ex> judge.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not warped or biased by prejudice; <as>as, an
<ex>unprejudiced</ex> judgment</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un*prej"u*diced*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms> <rj><au>V. Knox.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unprelated</ent>⟦br⟧
